		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Pictures of my homemade Famicom/NES converter.
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.54.org/condev/FC_NES_Conv/">http://www.54.org/condev/FC_NES_Conv/</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />Materials used:
<br />
<br />NES Cart (with all edge connecters)
<br />EDAC Cardedge Connectors 60P SOLDER TAIL 5.08mm ROW SPACE (mouser # 587-395-060
<br />IDE Cable (or floppy cable)
<br />8 470 ohm resistors

		

		</td>
	</tr>
